file.name: Property.yaml
file.content:
openapi: "3.0.0"
Property:
  type: object
  required:
    - token
  description: |
    Specifies the at_property via the token field. It can be used to control the scope for the delivery.
  properties:
    token:
      description: |
        The at_property token

        Validation
        * Required if the property is specified.
      type: string
